HEADWORD: infinite regression
<hw>infinite regression</hw></mhw>
<pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Philosophy, Logic)</fld> <def>A causal relationship
transmitted through an indefinite number of terms in a series, with no
term that begins the causal chain.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

